text: The 1989 Navy Midshipmen football team represented the United States Naval Academy (USNA) during the 1989 NCAA Division I-A football season. Navy competed as an independent with no conference affiliation. The team was led by third-year head coach Elliott Uzelac. ==Schedule== ==Personnel== ==Season summary== ===Army=== ==References== Navy Midshipmen Category:Navy Midshipmen football seasons Navy
